-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5단계 태그추가</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.velog.io/post-images/dooreplay/cc3a4f20-e036-11e9-8e95-fffafd57bcb8/image.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>key를 Name으로, 값은 프로젝트 이름으로 설정해준다!</p>\n<h4 id=\"6단계-보안-그룹-구성\"><a href=\"#6%EB%8B%A8%EA%B3%84-%EB%B3%B4%EC%95%88-%EA%B7%B8%EB%A3%B9-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"6단계 보안 그룹 구성 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6단계 보안 그룹 구성</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.velog.io/post-images/dooreplay/21024210-e037-11e9-a5fc-75251a85beee/image.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>매번 새로 만들 필요 없고 지난번에 만든 보안그룹 불러오기 하면 됨</p>\n<h4 id=\"7단계-검토\"><a href=\"#7%EB%8B%A8%EA%B3%84-%EA%B2%80%ED%86%A0\" aria-label=\"7단계 검토 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>7단계 검토</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.velog.io/post-images/dooreplay/536cc090-e037-11e9-b95d-93ba0d1a0cbf/image.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>나는 포트를 공용포트인 3000으로 설정해놨기 때문에 보안 경고가 뜨긴 하는데 무시 ㄱㄱ</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.velog.io/post-images/dooreplay/b719b850-e037-11e9-ad63-333d6909c4f1/image.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>기존 키 갖다쓰기 클릭하면…</p>\n<p>짠! Ec2서버가 두개 되었다!\n<img src=\"https://images.velog.io/post-images/dooreplay/f43dc4f0-e038-11e9-b95d-93ba0d1a0cbf/image.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>다시 우분투 서버 접속하기 <br />\n각자 경로와 ip주소에 맞게 아래의 명령어 바꾸기 !! 😆  <br />\n<code class=\"language-text\">ssh -i 다운로드/dooreplay.pem ubuntu@13.124.97.235</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.velog.io/post-images/dooreplay/5adcac80-e039-11e9-b95d-93ba0d1a0cbf/image.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>yes 하면 됨. 처음 접속하는 ip라서 일단 경고창 처럼 나오는 것.</p>\n<h2 id=\"node랑-다-설치하기\"><a href=\"#node%EB%9E%91-%EB%8B%A4-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"node랑 다 설치하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>node랑 다 설치하기</h2>\n<p>아래의 명령어 3개 고대로 입력하시면 됩니다~</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_10.x | sudo bash -</code>\n<code class=\"language-text\">sudo apt-get update</code>\n<code class=\"language-text\">sudo apt-get install nodejs</code></p>\n<p>(우분투 유저들을 위한 sudo 버전 ㅋㅋ!)</p>\n<h2 id=\"버전확인쓰\"><a href=\"#%EB%B2%84%EC%A0%84%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8%EC%93%B0\" aria-label=\"버전확인쓰 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>버전확인쓰</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.velog.io/post-images/dooreplay/496a50a0-e03a-11e9-b269-af6cf637a48e/image.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"project-clone\"><a href=\"#project-clone\" aria-label=\"project clone permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>project clone</h2>\n<p>다들 아는 방법쓰~ <code class=\"language-text\">git clone 프로젝트 깃 주소</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"npm-혹은-yarn-깔기\"><a href=\"#npm-%ED%98%B9%EC%9D%80-yarn-%EA%B9%94%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"npm 혹은 yarn 깔기 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>npm 혹은 yarn 깔기</h2>\n<p>지난번에 npm 깔았다 sass 문제가 생겼기 때문에 yarn 깔아주기\n<code class=\"language-text\">sudo apt-get install yarn</code>\nnpm 깔 사람은 <code class=\"language-text\">npm install</code>고고!</p>\n<p>이 블로그 참고해서 했음\n<a href=\"https://blkcoding.blogspot.com/2019/04/yarn-install-instead-of-cmdtest.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://blkcoding.blogspot.com/2019/04/yarn-install-instead-of-cmdtest.html</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"express\"><a href=\"#express\" aria-label=\"express permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>express</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add express</code> express를 프로젝트 폴더 내부에서 해줘야 함!</p>\n<h2 id=\"로컬-서버-바꿔주기\"><a href=\"#%EB%A1%9C%EC%BB%AC-%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EB%B0%94%EA%BF%94%EC%A3%BC%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"로컬 서버 바꿔주기 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>로컬 서버 바꿔주기</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">vi</code> 치고 i 눌러서 입력모드로 들어가기\n근데 여기서 잠깐! 제목을 입력 안해주면 안된다리</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">vi server.js</code> 라고 써주기\n<img src=\"https://images.velog.io/post-images/dooreplay/329dcca0-e03d-11e9-a5fc-75251a85beee/image.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">const express = require(&#39;express&#39;);\nconst path = require(&#39;path&#39;);\nconst env = process.env.ENV;\nconst app = express();\napp.get(&#39;/ping&#39;, function(req, res) {\n res.send(&#39;pong&#39;);\n});\napp.use(&#39;/&#39;, express.static(path.join(__dirname, &#39;build&#39;)));\napp.get(&#39;/*&#39;, function (req, res) {\n res.set({\n   &quot;Cache-Control&quot;: &quot;no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate&quot;,\n   &quot;Pragma&quot;: &quot;no-cache&quot;,\n   &quot;Date&quot;: new Date()\n });\n res.sendFile(path.join(__dirname, &#39;build&#39;, &#39;index.html&#39;));\n});\napp.listen(8080, () =&gt; {\n console.log(&#39;listening: &#39; + env);\n});</code></pre></div>\n<p>이거 쓴 다음에 밑에서 두번째 줄 port 8080->3000으로 바꾸기<br />\n(내가 ec2 port를 위에서 3000으로 설정해주었기 때문)</p>\n<h2 id=\"build\"><a href=\"#build\" aria-label=\"build permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>build</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">sudo yarn build</code> 해주고</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.velog.io/post-images/dooreplay/f615c700-e03d-11e9-8e95-fffafd57bcb8/image.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>뭔가 성공적인 느낌쓰…! 그래도 명령어를 또 입력해야 한다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">node server.js</code> server.js 파일을 읽어서 node가 돌아간것</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">nohup node server.js &amp;</code> 이걸 해줘야지 서버를 꺼도 주소창 입력하면 됨</p>\n<p>드디어 성공했슴다 오예!!!</p>\n<h2 id=\"추후-repo가-업데이트-되었다면\"><a href=\"#%EC%B6%94%ED%9B%84-repo%EA%B0%80-%EC%97%85%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8-%EB%90%98%EC%97%88%EB%8B%A4%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"추후 repo가 업데이트 되었다면 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>추후.. Repo가 업데이트 되었다면..</h2>\n<p>분명 최종본을 git에서 merge했는데 그게 안 뜬다!!\n그 이유는.. 나의 로컬 서버는 업데이트를 했지만 우분투 서버는 업데이트 해주지 않았기 때문 ㅠㅠ\n그럴땐..!</p>\n<ol>\n<li>우분투 서버 접속</li>\n<li>cd 명령어로 내 프로젝트 디렉토리에 접근</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">git pull origin master</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">sudo yarn build</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p>pull과 build까지 마치면 성공적으로 아마존 서버에 있는 작업물도 업데이트 할 수 있다!!<br /> 룰루~~♬</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/aws_ec2_re","tagSlugs":["/tag/aws/","/tag/project/","/tag/wecode/","/tag/위코드/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-11-06T15:38:23.169Z","description":"위코드 AWS 세션 때 EC2 서버 뚫기를 도전했다가 실패를 했고, 세션을 한 번 더 들은 이후 드디어 성공한 과정을 써본다.","tags":["aws","project","wecode","위코드"],"title":"AWS EC2 서버뚫기 성공기!"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/aws_ec2_re"}}}